---
description: "Service layer business logic rules"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Service Rules

- All business logic must be in Service layer
- Service orchestrates repositories

# Transactions
- Handle transaction in service (not repository)

# Validation
- Validate before calling repository

# Return
- Use DTO or Result pattern
- Do not return Entity directly

# Flow
1. Validate input
2. Start transaction
3. Call repository
4. Commit / rollback